root: ^Warlock: My dear Nannan... Actually, I still need one more thing.
^Nannan: Ahh! Don't come over here! You, you're... I’m going to tell my parents!
^Warlock: They agreed to this ages ago! Sacrificing you, a money sink, to save your little brother was the easiest decision they ever made!
^Warlock: Here, come here! Don’t make me get violent!
